&lt;p&gt;Guidelines for the use of headers in the Innovation theme:&lt;br /&gt;The theme uses HTML5 code with theme-specific CSS styling. To ensure proper HTML5 outlining, the use of h1 headers is reserved to the HTML body only; the page title is wrapped in an h2 header. You may use h3-h6 to create headers for your paragraphs in the page content area and h3 for headers in the sidebar area.&lt;/p&gt;
